            <p>
                Low-key mall with clothing shops, a food court & an amusement area with rides for kids.
            </p>
          
            <p></p>
            <p>Address&nbsp &nbsp:</p>
          
            <p>Kompleks Nagoya Citywalk, Lubuk Baja Kota, Kec. Lubuk Baja, Kota Batam, Kepulauan Riau 29444</p>
      
            <p>Call&nbsp &nbsp:</p>
          
            <p>(0778) 430000</p>
  
            <div class="button-container">
                <button type="button" class="btn" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#operationalhours">
                Operational Hours
