                                <ol>Wednesday : 11.00 - 21.00</ol>
                                <ol>Thursday : 11.00 - 21.00</ol>
                                <ol>Friday : 11.00 - 21.00</ol>
                                <ol>Saturday : 11.00 - 21.00</ol>
                                <ol>Sunday : 11.00 - 21.00</ol>
                            </li>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>          
            </div>
  
            <p></p>
            <p>Visit Web&nbsp &nbsp:</p>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/NagoyaCitywalk" target="_blank">Click Here</a>
        </div>
      
        <div class="container_frame">
            <iframe class="responsive-iframe" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Cv1ld2aRlE8" title="YouTube video player" >
            </iframe>
  
            <div class="ticket">
                <h4>Tickets</h4>
                <h6>Ticket &nbsp&nbsp:</h6>
                  <p>Starts From &nbsp&nbsp: IDR 100.000</p>
                <h6>Highlights &nbsp&nbsp:</h6>
                  <p>1. Get on rides that are fun for the whole family, like the Roller Coaster and the Bazooka Drop Zone Tower</p>
                  <p>2. Play educational and exciting games at the arcade machines</p>
                  <p>3. Top up your Funcard balance easily</p>
                  <p>4. Enjoy an excellent bonding opportunity that will bring your family closer than ever</p>
            </div> 
        </div>
      
        <div class="info-container">
            <div class="gmap_canvas">
                <iframe height="325" width="300" class="map" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3989.02336255853!2d104.00497766457241!3d1.1437742491657208!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31d989875a6cb14b%3A0xa73251c59be0f76f!2sFun%20World!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1632660312681!5m2!1sen!2sid" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0"></iframe>
